title: Preserve at Barton Creek - Luxury Estate - Available Now!
posting_body: Stunning Luxury Estate on 1.68 well-manicured acres with mature oaks in the prestigious gated community, Preserve at Barton Creek, with gorgeous hill country views backing to Barton Creek and zoned to Acclaimed Lake Travis ISD schools.
Grand impressive architectural design with Porte-cochere entry.
Entertainer's paradise with a resort style pool with waterfalls, spa, lighted sport court, outdoor kitchen (grill, Green Egg, sink), fire pit and guest quarters with cabana.
This home has every room you could want- a fully equipped home theater, game room w/bar, gym area, & 2 offices.
The soaring ceiling in the living room with a two story wall of windows captures the gorgeous preserve views.
The gourmet kitchen is fully equipped with commercial grade Thermador appliances, a large center island with breakfast bar, walk-in pantry, and butler's pantry.
Main Level: Grand Foyer Entry, 2 Offices, Open Kitchen/Living, Dining, Media Room, Bedroom w/En Suite Bathroom, Powder Room.
2nd Level: 5 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms, Game Room w/Bar, Laundry Room, Workout Room.
Lake Travis ISD bus pick up conveniently located within the gated community.
Close to shopping and restaurants at the Hill Country Galleria and only about 14 mi to downtown Austin and under 19 mi to the Austin Bergstrom International Airport.
Steps to the lower Barton Creek park-like setting.
Text Seth for more information or to schedule a showing!
Listing by Kristee Leonard, The Leaders Realty LLC
